---
Dockerfile is to create containerDisk image.
The image is configured in VMI manifest `spec.volumes.containerDisk.image`

With CentOS cloud image `CentOS-GenericCloud`, `mlx_core` driver will be
loaded automatically upon VM start, it saves time from installing
kernel-modules package and loading the driver manually.

CentOS cloud image can be downloaded from:
CentOS-7: https://cloud.centos.org/centos/7/images/
CentOS-8: https://cloud.centos.org/centos/8/x86_64/images/

`dpdk` pkg provides `testpmd` binary (used as test application).

`libibverbs` is a userspace library for using Mellanox device.


